%^RESET%^%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Prestige Class
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Shadow Adept:

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Requirements:%^RESET%^ Level 40 Character
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^             %^RESET%^ Level 20 Mage or Level 20 Sorcerer
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^             %^RESET%^ Faith: Lord Shadow
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^             %^RESET%^ 20 Base Intelligence or Charisma (before equipment modifiers)

%^RESET%^%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^For Mage Shadow Adepts:

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Races allowed:%^RESET%^ drow, elf, half-drow, half-elf, human, ogre-mage, gnome,
               yuan-ti
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Alignments allowed:%^RESET%^ any
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Cannot multiclass with:%^RESET%^ sorcerer, psion, psywarrior
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Hitdice:%^RESET%^ d6
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Saving throws:%^RESET%^ will strong, fort/reflex weak
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Class Skills:%^RESET%^ academics, dungeoneering, healing, spellcraft

%^RESET%^%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^For Sorcerer Shadow Adepts:

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Races allowed:%^RESET%^ human, half-elf, half-orc, half-drow, elf, drow, halfling, 
               gnome, voadkyn, kobold, goblin, orc (tanarukk), yuan-ti
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Alignments allowed:%^RESET%^ any
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Cannot multiclass with:%^RESET%^ mage, psion, psywarrior
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Hitdice:%^RESET%^ d6
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Saving throws:%^RESET%^ will strong, fort/reflex weak
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Class Skills:%^RESET%^ academics, disguise, influence, spellcraft
              **disguise temporarily substituted to perception until installed
      
%^RESET%^%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^For All Shadow Adepts:

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Class Feats:%^RESET%^
   %^RESET%^L1: gift of the shadows 
   %^RESET%^L4: elusive spellcraft
   %^RESET%^L7: shadow apotheosis

    %^RESET%^A shadow adept is a master not just of magic, but of its 
use by means of the secretive Shadow Weave, rather than the weave that 
nearly all arcanists use. Only Sharrans and their allies are privy to 
the hidden ways by which their Mistress' gift might be used.  A shadow 
adept is more familiar with certain spell types.  Enchantment, illusion 
and necromancy spells become easier for him to resist, and harder for 
his foes to resist.

